---
title: Chinese Beef Stir-Fry with Sichuan Sauce & Peanuts
description: Dive into a tasty bowl of quick-cooking beef strips tossed with colourful veggies and an easy sauce packed with umami flavours. It’s a takeaway standard made at home in a flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c859ddbc445fa4a8e66d022-2d1a2a7e.jpg
